18-- ----------------------
19-- $NamingConventions
20--
21--  Functions for relation-mapping operators are
22--  named under some conventions.
23--
24--  [@xxx-yyy@]       Name of relation-mapping operator.
25--
26--  [@consXxxYyy@]    Functions of 'Koshucode.Baala.Core.Relmap.Operator.RopCons'.
27--                    These functions make 'Koshucode.Baala.Core.Relmap.Relmap.Relmap'
28--                    from operator usages.
29--
30--  [@relmapXxxYyy@]  Functions from 'Koshucode.Baala.Core.Relmap.Relmap.Relmap'
31--                    to 'Koshucode.Baala.Core.Relmap.Relmap.Relmap'.
32--
33--  [@relkitXxxYyy@]  Functions that make 'Koshucode.Baala.Core.Relmap.Relkit.Relkit'.
34
